\newlabel{tab:res-baselines}{{5.17}{60}{Comparison with naïve baselines. Several LLM configurations underperform the majority baseline in accuracy while producing higher ECE, illustrating that inference-time LLM usage adds no value in cases where the model is dominated by evasion or mode collapse}{table.caption.32}{}}
