\newlabel{tab:res-composite}{{5.18}{61}{Composite utility score across the twelve configurations. The score integrates macro-F1, calibration quality ($1 - \ece $), and prediction diversity (normalized entropy). Configurations with mode collapse receive utility scores close to zero, correctly capturing their lack of practical usefulness}{table.caption.33}{}}
